288
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:10,799
Mr. Liu.

289
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:11,960
Hurry.

290
00:20:13,279 --> 00:20:13,839
Let's go.

291
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,039
Looking for Qu Meng?

292
00:20:26,590 --> 00:20:27,400
What are you holding?

293
00:20:32,279 --> 00:20:33,359
I came to return clothes.

294
00:20:33,599 --> 00:20:34,759
You came all the way here

295
00:20:34,759 --> 00:20:35,880
just to return clothes?

296
00:20:40,799 --> 00:20:41,880
Let me check.

297
00:20:46,519 --> 00:20:49,319
I promised her to write a poem for her.

298
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:51,920
I want her to see it.

299
00:20:52,839 --> 00:20:54,079
You already set up a meeting.

300
00:20:54,440 --> 00:20:55,759
