301
00:20:56,119 --> 00:20:58,079
Qu Meng really has sharp eyes for men.

302
00:20:58,440 --> 00:20:59,920
I knew you'd be meddling secretly.

303
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:07,160
She told me to wait for you here.

304
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:09,920
It's too shaky.

305
00:21:10,079 --> 00:21:10,960
Help me a bit.

306
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:12,759
Help me.

307
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:14,640
Ms. He.

308
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:17,640
Let me hold. I can't walk steadily.

309
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,960
Why are you so shy?

310
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,480
Never had a girl hold you?

311
00:21:33,359 --> 00:21:35,200
Distinguished guests.

312
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:37,599
Good evening, everyone.

313
00:21:37,599 --> 00:21:40,480
Welcome to the International Club.

314
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:43,799
- Good.
- Good.

315
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:44,720
First,

316
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:47,160
