320
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:56,759
This is thanks to your support.

321
00:21:56,759 --> 00:21:58,020
She told you not to overthink it.

322
00:21:58,359 --> 00:21:59,799
That ball is just for show.

323
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:04,200
Like those flashy people

324
00:22:04,359 --> 00:22:05,559
who all wear suits.

325
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:07,720
They're not as comfy
as tanks and shorts.

326
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,240
It's just about style.

327
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:10,880
I saw everything.

328
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,359
This ball

329
00:22:24,599 --> 00:22:25,559
is for the lucky draw.

330
00:22:26,799 --> 00:22:27,559
Yes.

331
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:28,759
A lucky draw.

332
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,210
We're drawing today too.

333
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:35,880
We've specially prepared
a lucky draw for you.

334
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,599
We'll have the results soon.
Try your luck.

335
00:22:37,599 --> 00:22:39,960
There are three prize tiers.

336
00:22:40,119 --> 00:22:40,720
Take this.

337
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,720
Want a drink? I'll get you one.

338
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:43,930
Give me a second.

339
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,400
1,000 yuan in cash.

340
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:50,319
With the Fu character, second prize.

341
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:52,799
A gold bracelet.

342
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,440
Here comes the exciting part.

343
00:22:58,599 --> 00:22:59,640
With the Ya character,

344
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:03,319
first prize, a Rolex gold watch.

345
00:23:03,559 --> 00:23:05,079
A gold Rolex.

346
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:22,519
Today, we've also prepared
a special prize.

347
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:24,880
The special prize is

348
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:29,240
to sing a duet with our club's
Golden Ball Angel,

349
00:23:29,599 --> 00:23:31,599
Qu Meng.

350
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,599
So who drew the Golden Ball?

351
00:23:34,839 --> 00:23:36,079
Where's the Golden Ball?

352
00:23:36,839 --> 00:23:38,240
Where's the Golden Ball?

353
00:23:38,359 --> 00:23:40,839
Where's the Golden Ball?

354
00:23:40,839 --> 00:23:41,839
Here it is!

355
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:45,640
Hurry up. Stand up.

356
00:23:46,319 --> 00:23:48,319
Let's congratulate him.

357
00:23:48,319 --> 00:23:50,119
Congratulations.

358
00:23:50,119 --> 00:23:52,480
Good. How lucky.

359
00:23:54,290 --> 00:23:55,480
Move. Don't just stand there.

360
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:56,960
Go on. Get on it.

361
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:58,519
Get on it. Go.

362
00:23:58,519 --> 00:23:59,880
Hurry. Go on.

363
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:02,319
Qu Meng's waiting there. Go.

364
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:04,080
Congratulations.

365
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:06,039
Don't be shy, young man.

366
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:07,559
- Go on.
- Get up there.

367
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:09,599
- Get up there.
- Get up there.

368
00:24:09,799 --> 00:24:10,839
- Go on.
- Go on.

369
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,440
- Hurry up.
- Hurry.

370
00:24:19,799 --> 00:24:21,160
- Go on.
- Go on.

371
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:32,519
- Sing one.
- Sing one.

372
00:24:32,519 --> 00:24:36,400
- Good.
- Good.

373
00:24:46,620 --> 00:24:53,460
♪Sweet as honey. Your smile is sweet♪

374
00:24:53,820 --> 00:24:59,300
♪Like flowers blooming in spring breeze♪

375
00:24:59,300 --> 00:25:03,460
♪Blooming in spring breeze♪

376
00:25:05,420 --> 00:25:12,380
♪Where was it? Where did I see you?♪

377
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:17,620
♪Your smile feels so familiar♪

378
00:25:17,980 --> 00:25:22,380
♪I just can't recall it♪

379
00:25:41,599 --> 00:25:42,359
Hello.

380
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:50,160
Singing lady.

381
00:25:53,079 --> 00:25:53,880
Hello.

382
00:25:55,519 --> 00:25:58,240
When the neon river flood the banks,

383
00:25:59,039 --> 00:26:00,279
your laughter

384
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:02,599
is the sail that won't sink.

385
00:26:04,119 --> 00:26:07,000
When distant starlight cuts the clouds,

386
00:26:08,319 --> 00:26:09,440
your singing

387
00:26:09,799 --> 00:26:11,640
is an untamed flame.

388
00:26:13,359 --> 00:26:14,279
Don't be afraid.

389
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:17,880
The nightingale also waited in thorns,

390
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:21,400
just to sing defiant notes.

391
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:23,680
Don't be afraid.

392
00:26:25,039 --> 00:26:27,559
Seeds break through ruins to rise,

393
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:31,400
only to pierce the pain and take root.

394
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:36,079
Every grain of dust will awaken.

395
00:26:37,119 --> 00:26:39,640
Every soul is surging.

396
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:43,000
Light will cross a thousand years.

397
00:26:44,119 --> 00:26:46,559
Flowers will eventually
bloom before our eyes.

398
00:26:48,119 --> 00:26:49,519
Between light and flowers,

399
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:51,680
I saw your tears.

400
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:54,480
They shimmer

401
00:26:55,559 --> 00:26:58,759
and shatter into stars in neon.

402
00:27:00,279 --> 00:27:00,920
Hello.

403
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:04,519
Miss.

404
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:08,279
Hello.

405
00:27:16,160 --> 00:27:21,160
- Good.
- Good.

406
00:27:23,759 --> 00:27:26,480
- Good.
- Good.

407
00:27:37,119 --> 00:27:37,920
Talk.

408
00:27:38,559 --> 00:27:40,200
What was tonight about?

409
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:43,400
Reciting poems too. It's quite novel.

410
00:27:44,039 --> 00:27:46,079
Mr. Xu, this is on me.

411
00:27:46,910 --> 00:27:47,960
I didn't think it through.

412
00:27:48,519 --> 00:27:50,200
This isn't the time to blame.

413
00:27:51,119 --> 00:27:53,440
We're family. Fix this first.

414
00:27:54,079 --> 00:27:54,920
It's no big deal.

415
00:27:55,319 --> 00:27:57,559
He probably didn't get the trick.

416
00:27:58,039 --> 00:28:00,519
He saw the raffle earlier.

417
00:28:00,839 --> 00:28:01,920
He's just curious.

418
00:28:02,319 --> 00:28:03,319
It's fine now.

419
00:28:03,640 --> 00:28:05,359
People like him has no backing.

420
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,400
Give him cash and send him off.

421
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:08,799
You think money is easy to make?

422
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:10,319
He caused trouble without spending.

423
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:12,359
We earned this on knife edges.

424
00:28:12,359 --> 00:28:13,480
You just give it away?

425
00:28:16,279 --> 00:28:16,960
Mr. Xu.

426
00:28:24,039 --> 00:28:24,559
Here.

427
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,759
Apologize to Mr. Xu.

428
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:30,920
I caused this.

429
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:33,079
I'll handle it.

430
00:28:33,960 --> 00:28:34,680
Where is he?

431
00:28:36,610 --> 00:28:37,319
He was sent away.

432
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,359
He's gone?

433
00:28:39,839 --> 00:28:41,440
No one saw him leave.

434
00:29:21,480 --> 00:29:23,599
Yang Wen... Yang Wenyuan.

435
00:29:32,519 --> 00:29:33,839
Qu Meng wears this too.

436
00:29:35,079 --> 00:29:36,079
Do you all do this?

437
00:29:37,839 --> 00:29:38,759
Does she do this too?

438
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:40,359
Get lost.

439
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:43,000
You were forced, right?

440
00:29:43,319 --> 00:29:44,440
Go.

441
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:47,920
It's too late.

442
00:30:27,319 --> 00:30:28,599
(People are divided into ranks.)

443
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,500
(We're not from the same world.)

444
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:32,390
(Don't ask what you shouldn't.)

445
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,799
(Don't come)

446
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,150
(to places like this again.)

447
00:30:40,559 --> 00:30:41,240
Yang Wenyuan!

448
00:30:44,039 --> 00:30:46,240
(Binchuan Police Shunyang Road Station)
Stop. What are you doing?

449
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,559
I came looking for you,

450
00:30:49,599 --> 00:30:51,799
just wanting to see
what the club is all about.

451
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:55,279
Now there's no need.

452
00:30:56,799 --> 00:30:57,480
It won't work.

453
00:30:58,200 --> 00:31:00,000
The police have checked many times,

454
00:31:00,279 --> 00:31:01,880
but no one dares tell the truth.

455
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,599
Don't get yourself involved.

456
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:06,000
Stop it. Go back with me.

457
00:31:09,279 --> 00:31:10,240
What are you doing?

458
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:13,720
Not coming back?

459
00:31:26,630 --> 00:31:27,559
Are you leaving or not?

460
00:31:27,839 --> 00:31:28,359
Sir.

461
00:31:29,559 --> 00:31:30,319
Is there a problem?

462
00:31:39,839 --> 00:31:41,559
What are you doing? Look at yourself.

463
00:31:42,039 --> 00:31:43,039
Stop it, you...

464
00:31:44,359 --> 00:31:46,160
You even made the police come out.

465
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:47,839
Sir.

466
00:31:48,519 --> 00:31:49,839
How about you talk inside?

467
00:31:56,799 --> 00:31:57,599
We're fine.

468
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:58,920
Sorry.

469
00:32:00,599 --> 00:32:02,720
Alright, that's enough.

470
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:04,480
Give me a hug.

471
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,680
They've fallen in love.

472
00:32:40,799 --> 00:32:41,359
Let's go.

473
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:52,880
We searched everywhere.

474
00:32:53,119 --> 00:32:54,519
This guy didn't hide anything.

475
00:33:17,119 --> 00:33:18,119
Are you doing it too?

476
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,279
Get up.

477
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,680
Get up!

478
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,200
Okay.

479
00:33:45,799 --> 00:33:47,039
I provoked you first.

480
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,400
Consider it my compensation.

481
00:33:53,359 --> 00:33:54,240
Qu Meng, don't do this.

482
00:33:54,839 --> 00:33:55,759
I said, don't do this.

483
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:56,720
Don't do this.

484
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:01,119
You think I'm dirty?

485
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:21,559
Yang Wenyuan,
you have no right to think we're dirty.

486
00:34:22,559 --> 00:34:24,480
Do you know what it's like

487
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:25,800
to have no money to feed yourself?

488
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:28,519
I was the third girl in my family.

489
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:33,599
In ninth grade, my mom left.

490
00:34:35,199 --> 00:34:37,199
My stepfather sold my eldest sister.

491
00:34:38,119 --> 00:34:39,280
One day, my second sister

492
00:34:39,660 --> 00:34:41,719
suddenly went with him
to the city to buy medicine

493
00:34:41,719 --> 00:34:43,199
and never returned.

494
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:53,960
I escaped alone

495
00:34:55,519 --> 00:34:56,559
and came to Binchuan.

496
00:34:58,360 --> 00:35:00,360
At first, I worked in a small restaurant

497
00:35:00,719 --> 00:35:01,559
as a waitress.

498
00:35:02,719 --> 00:35:03,679
One day,

499
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:06,800
a group of men
suddenly started groping me.

500
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:07,590
I refused to comply.

501
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,280
They took advantage of my drunkenness,

502
00:35:10,290 --> 00:35:12,480
locked me in a private room,
and raped me.

503
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,159
I made a scene,

504
00:35:14,559 --> 00:35:16,559
so they falsely accused me of stealing.

505
00:35:17,079 --> 00:35:18,719
Eventually, they threw me in jail.

506
00:35:20,199 --> 00:35:21,000
Well?

507
00:35:21,679 --> 00:35:23,880
Not what you imagined, right?

508
00:35:28,639 --> 00:35:31,199
You think I was born wanting that job?

509
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:34,679
Am I born that lowly?

510
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,880
Yes, we were young and naive,

511
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:40,119
being led in like headless flies.

512
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:42,960
We thought we found a shortcut
and thought we could still get out.

513
00:35:43,079 --> 00:35:44,510
But once you're on the thief's ship,

514
00:35:45,599 --> 00:35:46,719
there's no getting off.

515
00:35:49,039 --> 00:35:50,039
I can help you.

516
00:35:50,039 --> 00:35:50,960
How?

517
00:35:52,010 --> 00:35:53,190
I'll take you away from here.

518
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,840
I work in the club.

519
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,079
Who would let me go?

520
00:36:09,519 --> 00:36:11,119
Since you're already involved,

521
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:14,280
we can only use their methods.

522
00:36:17,239 --> 00:36:18,159
Leave Binchuan.

523
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,159
The club,

524
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:23,639
what we are, and what we do

525
00:36:23,639 --> 00:36:24,400
doesn't matter.

526
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:27,320
Our roots were ground away long ago.

527
00:36:27,900 --> 00:36:28,920
We're asleep for too long.

528
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,800
We can't wake up.

529
00:36:31,119 --> 00:36:32,079
A poor poet like you

530
00:36:32,599 --> 00:36:33,880
shouldn't imagine using us

531
00:36:34,079 --> 00:36:35,559
to satisfy your idealism.

532
00:36:36,599 --> 00:36:37,880
All your self-indulgent words

533
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:39,480
only cause trouble for others.

534
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,639
They're useless.

535
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:43,119
I'd say stop dreaming here.

536
00:36:44,159 --> 00:36:44,760
Take the money,

537
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,119
write your lousy poems,

538
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,150
and don't come back for me.

539
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:52,480
It won't end well.

540
00:37:05,719 --> 00:37:06,440
Go back.

541
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,039
I said,

542
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:11,880
go back.

543
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:16,719
Get lost!

544
00:37:28,039 --> 00:37:29,199
Just discipling him.

545
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:30,920
Watch your limits.

546
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:57,320
In other people's eyes,

547
00:37:58,519 --> 00:38:00,199
I'm just a convict for life.

548
00:38:00,559 --> 00:38:02,280
My life is a dump.

549
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:03,519
You're a great poet.

550
00:38:03,519 --> 00:38:04,780
I'm not worth you picking trash.

551
00:38:04,790 --> 00:38:05,679
Do you understand?

552
00:38:17,800 --> 00:38:18,920
When I got out,

553
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:22,079
Ms. Hong brought me to the club.

554
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:26,320
(Binchuan Correctional Institution)
But it wasn't at all what I imagined.

555
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:29,480
You think I didn't resist?

556
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:32,039
You think I wanted to live like this?

557
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:34,519
In your eyes, I saw

558
00:38:34,519 --> 00:38:36,000
my former self.

559
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,079
Dreams in my heart.

560
00:38:39,519 --> 00:38:40,480
Light in my eyes.

561
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:16,519
Why hasn't the driver returned yet?

562
00:39:18,039 --> 00:39:18,639
Meng.

563
00:39:19,119 --> 00:39:20,719
You seem worried.

564
00:39:23,239 --> 00:39:24,800
If you're unhappy at the club,

565
00:39:25,559 --> 00:39:27,880
tell me anytime. I'll get you a new job.

566
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:33,880
Do you know
why I like listening to you sing?

567
00:39:34,679 --> 00:39:36,679
When you sing "Sweet as Honey", it's...

568
00:39:37,079 --> 00:39:44,000
♪Sweet as honey. Your smile is sweet♪

569
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:49,199
I always feel my vocal technique
and breath control are lacking.

570
00:39:49,599 --> 00:39:51,360
Touch it. My breath...

